\ncore masses and the total mass of the star.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Jun 2020 18:51:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Jul 2020 15:30:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-20"}
