 to kernel density estimation (KDE),\nour algorithm not only reveals more detailed density changes, but also fits\nunseen data better, as measured by the log-likelihood.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Jun 2020 19:19:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Oct 2020 12:11:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 18 Jul 2022 14:54:14 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 9 Dec 2022 10:05:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-12"}
