ars are in fact active, they should all\ncontribute to this sample of lithium-rich giants at some level.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Jun 2020 08:54:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 May 2021 09:48:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-26"}
