ental results demonstrate that these\nfeatures are useful in inductive graph classification tasks with no increase to\nthe number of parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Jun 2020 12:51:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-04"}
