in the CME magnetic structure with\nmulti-spacecraft measurements, indicating that modelled FDs reflect well the\nCME evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Jun 2020 13:13:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-05"}
