erivatives, reducing the damage caused by\nthe instantaneous impact of high pulse electric-currents, enhancing the\nanti-interference ability of electronic equipments to resist the high pulse\nelectric-currents and their current derivatives. Further the second-force\nequilibrium equation is able to explain two types of superconducting currents.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Jun 2020 13:46:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-05"}
